    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You are trained in the native weaponry of your homeland. You gain access to the weaponry of your homeland - the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Y1dkRsRd1Z7Jf2y6]{Katana}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.YOpopjoWgU7bkmwh]{Wakizashi} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.KtarUneAx0hibGtW]{Nodachi}, as well as the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.LxqA4VC4np2RLkQb]{Butchering Axe} as a Xaela, or the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.NufKswitJjxDCX8f]{Naginata} as a Raen. For the purposes of proficiency, you treat any of these that are martial weapons as simple weapons and any that are advanced weapons as martial weapons.</p><p>At 5th level, whenevver you gain a critical hit with one of these weapons, you get its critical specialization effect.</p>",
